data.description: Charming Nokomis bungalow has been entirely updated within the last 10 years. Great location close to parks, shops and trails. The open kitchen  has sunlight streaming inside thru the french doors and a newer microwave and dishwasher. The kitchen opens  into the dining room with the gorgeous built in’s and slate tile. Main floor primary bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry with pedestal washer and bonus office/den finish off the main level. Two additional bedrooms upstairs add to this perfect space. Freshly painted over the summer of 2023 all you need to do is move in. The floor plan has a great flow come see for yourself.
